question: how many products were sold in 2017
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2017-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2017-12-31'

question: how many products are sold with prices greater than 200 dollars in 2017
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID JOIN PRODUCTS AS T3 on T2.PRODUCT_ID  =  T3.PRODUCT_ID where T3.PRICE  >  200 and T1.DATE  >=  '2017-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2017-12-31'

question: what are the products that were sold in 2012
query: select distinct T2.PRODUCT_ID from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2012-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2012-12-31'

question: what products were sold from January 2012 to April 2012
query: select distinct T2.PRODUCT_ID from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2012-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2012-04-30'

question: how many products were sold between 2011 and 2015
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2011-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2015-12-31'

question: which customer bought products between 2010 and 2013
query: select distinct SALES.CUSTOMER_ID from SALES where SALES.DATE  >=  '2010-01-01' and SALES.DATE  <=  '2013-12-31'

question: How many customers bought GALAZY since January 2014
query: select count ( distinct T3.CUSTOMER_ID )  from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T3.DATE  >=  '2014-01-01' and T1.TYPE  =  'GALAZY'

question: how many IFONEs were sold since October 2013 in shops located in New York
query: select distinct sum ( T3.QUANTITY )  from SHOPS AS T1 JOIN SALES AS T2 on T1.SHOP_ID  =  T2.SHOP_ID JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID JOIN PRODUCTS AS T4 on T3.PRODUCT_ID  =  T4.PRODUCT_ID where T2.DATE  >=  '2013-10-01' and T4.TYPE  =  'IFONE' and T1.ADDRESS  =  'New York'

question: how many products were sold before October 2018 in San Francisco
query: select distinct sum ( T3.QUANTITY )  from SHOPS AS T1 JOIN SALES AS T2 on T1.SHOP_ID  =  T2.SHOP_ID JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T2.DATE  <  '2018-10-01' and T1.ADDRESS  =  'San Francisco'

question: how many products with prices from 100 to 400 were sold
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID where T1.PRICE  >=  100 and T1.PRICE  <=  400

question: which ANAPPLE products did customers buy in 2017
query: select distinct T3.PRODUCT_ID from MANUFACTURERS AS T1 JOIN PRODUCTS AS T2 on T1.MANUFACTURER_ID  =  T2.MANUFACTURER_ID JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T3 on T2.PRODUCT_ID  =  T3.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T4 on T3.SALES_ID  =  T4.SALES_ID where T4.DATE  >=  '2017-01-01' and T4.DATE  <=  '2017-12-31' and T1.NAME  =  'ANAPPLE'

question: how many products did customers buy before 2018 with price between 200 and 1000
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T3.DATE  <  '2018-01-01' and T1.PRICE  >=  200 and T1.PRICE  <=  1000

question: how many products were sold between 2011 and 2012
query: select distinct sum ( T2.QUANTITY )  from SALES AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T1.DATE  >=  '2011-01-01' and T1.DATE  <=  '2012-12-31'

question: what is the amount of sales made in 2015
query: select distinct sum ( SALES.SUM_TOTAL )  from SALES where SALES.DATE  >=  '2015-01-01' and SALES.DATE  <=  '2015-12-31'

question: what is the quantity of sales made in 2016 per sales
query: select distinct sum ( T1.QUANTITY )  , T2.SALES_ID from SALES_DETAILS AS T1 JOIN SALES AS T2 on T1.SALES_ID  =  T2.SALES_ID where T2.DATE  >=  '2016-01-01' and T2.DATE  <=  '2016-12-31' group by T2.SALES_ID

question: how many sales were made in May 2014
query: select count ( distinct SALES.SALES_ID )  from SALES where SALES.DATE  >=  '2014-05-01' and SALES.DATE  <=  '2014-05-31'

question: show the customers who bought IFONE after 2010
query: select distinct T3.CUSTOMER_ID from PRODUCTS AS T1 JOIN SALES_DETAILS AS T2 on T1.PRODUCT_ID  =  T2.PRODUCT_ID JOIN SALES AS T3 on T2.SALES_ID  =  T3.SALES_ID where T3.DATE  >  '2010-12-31' and T1.TYPE  =  'IFONE'

question: what is the total amount of VERZN sales in 2015
query: select distinct sum ( T2.SUM_TOTAL )  from VENDORS AS T1 JOIN SALES AS T2 on T1.VENDOR_ID  =  T2.VENDOR_ID where T2.DATE  >=  '2015-01-01' and T2.DATE  <=  '2015-12-31' and T1.NAME  =  'VERZN'

question: what are the ANAPPLE products that were sold in 2014

question: show the sales per shop in 2018
